description:
The company is interested in a motivated and enthusiastic student, who will be engaged in the following duties: 
 - Learning and implementing the main working principles, structural functions and NSS/BSS/BTS subsystems of the GSM/WCDMA networks;
 - Testing of the GSM/WCDMA networks;
 - Monitoring, planning and testing of the GSM radio network settings;
 - Performing statistical data analysis of BSS subsystem;

 The detailed work-plan will be sent upon receipt of nomination documents.
